exceptions.exn: In environment p : nat Hp : p <> 0 x, y : Z_Zp H : proj1_sig x = proj1_sig y a : nat p1, p2 : a < p Unable to unify "p2" with "p1".
In environment p : nat Hp : p <> 0 x, y : Z_Zp H : proj1_sig x = proj1_sig y a : nat p1, p2 : a < p Unable to unify "proj1_sig x = proj1_sig y" with "p1 = p2".

original: intros x y H. apply eq_sig_hprop. intros a p1 p2. reflexivity. apply H.
